    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AUTOGUN HEROES 进入超级充能模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328730/extras/ba4533ac16ed4b1c8ddad58d2193f7af.poster.avif?t=1759825682\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328730/extras/ba4533ac16ed4b1c8ddad58d2193f7af.webm?t=1759825682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328730/extras/ba4533ac16ed4b1c8ddad58d2193f7af.mp4?t=1759825682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >外星人已经占领了整个银河系，而你的任务就是与Gus和他的英雄团队一起夺回它！Autogun Heroes: Supercharged是一款激动人心的射击游戏，结合了基于技能的2D动作平台和紧致、响应迅速的操控。组建你的英雄团队，每位英雄都有独特的能力，一场战斗一场战斗地收复你的家园！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择你的游戏风格，选择你的英雄</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328730/extras/6c2381a5026915edaa3c975a69590575.poster.avif?t=1759825682\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328730/extras/6c2381a5026915edaa3c975a69590575.webm?t=1759825682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328730/extras/6c2381a5026915edaa3c975a69590575.mp4?t=1759825682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一支多样化的英雄阵容中组建你的团队，每个英雄都拥有独特的能力，从加快射速到喷气背包不等。尝试不同的英雄，并根据你的游戏风格战略性地选择最喜欢的英雄。为了增强英雄的优势并弥补他们的弱点，你还可以通过武器、装备和护甲进一步优化他们的表现，自定义伤害、射速和防御等属性，以适应被外星人占领的银河系的无尽挑战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用武器、护甲和装备进行优化</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328730/extras/7ae82a56270ebb4660f455263b6ea211.poster.avif?t=1759825682\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328730/extras/7ae82a56270ebb4660f455263b6ea211.webm?t=1759825682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328730/extras/7ae82a56270ebb4660f455263b6ea211.mp4?t=1759825682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择能够增强每个角色独特属性的武器、装备和护甲，以最大化他们对抗外星人的潜力。最佳装备搭配取决于你的游戏风格——通过尝试找到能够完美补充你的策略并轻松应对未来挑战的理想组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wishlist 现在！</strong></p>",
